Find information about diabetes, obesity, cancer, asthma, and many other consumer health topics.


Precision Medicine Initiative

Learn about a research effort to revolutionize how we improve health and treat disease.


Rigor and Reproducibility

Learn how NIH is enhancing rigor and reproducibility in scientific research.


Clinical Trials and You

Learn about participating in clinical trials and where to find them.


Voices of the NIH Community

NIH is launching a project to capture an oral history of the research experience. Learn how you can participate!


The BRAIN Initiative

Learn about a new Presidential focus aimed at revolutionizing our understanding of the human brain.


Impact of NIH Research

Learn how NIH-supported research has had a major positive impact on nearly all of our lives.


Diversity

Find out about the "Enhancing the Diversity of the NIH-funded Workforce" Program.


Accelerating Medicines Partnership

